title: Spellbook_Acquire
---
Hey, it’s Wiz’s spellbook!
Looks like we’ll need a couple things to finish the spell…
Pluck a bloom for petaled paws,
Sharpen them with gemstone claws,
Prop them up with shards of bone,
And thy famil’ar shall be done.
Doesn’t really work when read out loud, but I guess it’ll do.
===
